  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Both light and exercise are effective countermeasures for space and ground-based crews for
      circadian phase resetting and alertness levels. The investigators propose to test the
      combined effects of these two countermeasures to determine whether adding exercise to light
      stimuli will further improve circadian phase resetting and alertness.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
